text:
el naturópata, la naturópata
This means that the noun can be masculine or feminine, depending on the gender of person it refers to (e.g. el doctor, la doctora).
masculine or feminine noun 1. (profession) a. naturopath Elisa consultó con un naturópata, quien le recetó remedios naturales para tratar sus problemas de salud. Elisa had an appointment with a naturopath, who prescribed natural remedies to address her health concerns. Copyright © Curiosity Media Inc. naturópata
